{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"傷哉！每個誹謗者, 詆毀者"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他聚積財產, 而當作武器"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他以為他的財產, 能使他不滅。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"絕不然, 他必定要被投在毀滅坑中。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你怎能知道毀滅坑是什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"是真主的燃著的烈活。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"能升到人的心上。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他們必定要被關在烈火中"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"吊在許多很高的柱子上。"}]}